description.0: Radioactive Man has captured Spider-Man! Only Iron Man possesses the power to rescue Spidey from Radioactive Man's deadly, and unusually cruel, experiments.
description.2: Cannonball struggles not to use his mutant powers at a Lila Cheney concert…especially when Spyder abducts his headlining ladylove!
description.3: The Star Child begins its journey as the new Star Brand! However, its father Ken decides he isn't quite done being the Star Brand just yet!
description.4: Hogun lies comatose in the hospital, but that doesn't stop an unwelcome visit from the sinister Seth! Meanwhile, Balder makes a crucial decision for the fate of Thor and Asgard...
description.6: Seeking Apocalypse's sentient ship, a group of shapeshifting aliens wears the faces of prominent Avengers… and seek to disassemble X-Factor!
description.8: The search for the Beyonders is on! Destination- the Negative Zone! But the Fantastic Four won't be able to navigate the treacherous dimension alone, and they'll need to get help from the most unlikely of places- Doctor Doom!
description.9: The X-Men are in Colorado dealing with a rampant Brood outbreak. Meanwhile, Madelyne Pryor has a vision that may spell the end for her and Cyclops.
description.10: Silver Surfer, along with the Fantastic Four’s Mr. Fantastic and Invisible Woman, must plunge into the heart of a black hole to save Galactus!
description.11: Meet Robbie Baldwin, a boy who has all the problems of a normal teenager, but with one exception - he's secretly the super hero Speedball!'
description.12: Moses Magnum has issued an ultimatum to the government of Japan: Turn absolute power over to him, or he will use his Magnum Force to sink the entire country!
description.13: Peter Parker's book of Spider-Man photos is hitting stores, and Peter's off touring the country to promote it! But fun turns to danger when the web-slinger encounters that gentleman thief, the Black Fox, in sunny California!
description.14: The Black Fox has stolen a valuable chalice. And if the wall-crawling wonder can't recover it, his wife will die!
description.15: Seeing Thor as her ultimate threat, Nebula unleashes a dinosaur robot from the future and sets it on Thor's trail. Can the God of Thunder stop this future menace?
description.16: When the Watchdogs kidnap Captain America's parents, he sets out to rescue them - even if he has to kill the Watchdogs to do it! Meanwhile, the Captain surrenders to the commission that stripped him of his name and costume!
description.24: Hawkeye sets his sights on stopping terrorists in LA!
description.26: The team's struggle against Quicksilver continues! And they have no idea what's coming for them next!
description.30: Spidey continues his search for Tombstone, but he soon discovers he's not alone in his search. Someone else has Tombstone in his sights, and he's not the type to show mercy! Watch out, Tombstone, the Punisher is on your trail!
description.31: Silver Surfer vs. Silver Surfer? One’s an imposter, one’s the real deal. And by the end of this issue, only one will stand triumphant!
description.32: The Punisher guest-stars! Vigilantism takes two extremes, as Daredevil tries to prevent Punisher from enacting his "eye for an eye" method. But no one stands in Frank Castle's way, especially the Man Without Fear!
description.33: Clay Quartermain, Rick Jones and Betty Banner explain the details of what happened to a jury. Meanwhile, S.H.I.E.L.D. soldiers find dust where the Hulk's body should be...
description.34: Iron Man must stop a Stane International satellite that is plummeting towards Earth. Afterwards, Tony shows off his new armor at a Stark Enterprises show, while Ant-Man stops a band of murderers from killing civilians in the audience.
description.35: Magik is pushed to the murderous brink in her Limbo battle against Forge! This could be a Sorcerer's Duel… to the death!
description.36: Thor's headed for the silver screen! Scriptwriter Maddie Arnstein is tasked to write a story for a film about the Thunder God, and leads us on a wild ride of romance and what-ifs!
description.38: Iceman is at risk of becoming Infectia's mindless slave… and Beast and the kids may be powerless to stop her!
description.40: The Fantastic Four find themselves back in space almost as soon as they got home! But this time, it's to uncover the secrets of an alien conspiracy that even crosses dimensions! Plus, can the two Things find comfort in one another?
description.41: Colossus and Psylocke battle the Brood!
description.42: When the X-Men arrive in Japan, they find that the city Agarashima is ablaze by a great firestorm caused by an unnatural earthquake! Only one mutant can help them now...their old ally, SUNFIRE!
description.51: The newlyweds must make a pivotal decision- move to Kansas for Peter's new job, or stay in New York for MJ's burgeoning career? Silver Sable calls on Spider-Man and Sandman to take down neo-Nazi Franz Kraus once and for all!
description.52: Because of the Ebony Blade's blood curse, Black Knight must don an exoskeleton to prevent further paralysis. After the battle with Marrina, Captain Marvel reverts to her human self and is severely weakened. And the mystery member of the Kang Korps is revealed!
description.53: The President has been turned into a giant snake! Will Captain America be able to save the free world from the Serpent Society? Or will the Serpent Society usher in a new world order?
description.54: The entire team versus the wrath of the Bogeyman! Guest-starring Rebecca Littlehale.
description.55: Before the West Coast Avengers can even catch their breath from their last fight, they become captives of the deadly foe…QUICKSILVER!? What has caused the once-noble Avenger to turn on his comrades, including his own sister?
description.60: The Star Child does the unthinkable - by taking away Ken's Star Brand! What will this cost Ken, and what does the child plan to do with it?
description.61: Joe Robertson is bedridden in the hospital, gravely injured in his encounter with Tombstone. Shaken to his core, Peter Parker embarks on a solemn misson: find Tombstone and make him answer to justice, at any cost!
description.62: Ronan the Accuser comes to Nenora’s aid after a band of soldiers attempt mutiny. How much longer can the Skrull imposter maintain her ruse? Surfer finds a moment to mourn the death of Mantis, but is invigorated by a new mission- finding her son!
description.63: Things are heating up between Matt and Mary- but what happens if Karen Page discovers her boyfriend's tryst? Daredevil's disgusted by his new foe Typhoid...and he can't get enough.
description.64: The Leader selects the small village of Middletown to detonate the gamma rays bomb he made Rock and Redentor steal from the government.
description.65: Magik gains the support of her fellow New Mutants in her mission against Forge. But before Illyana takes on the technomancer, she and the team must contend with Freedom Force!
description.66: Thor's battle against Quicksand takes a dire turn, when a nuclear plant starts to go into meltdown!
description.68: Cyclops and Jean Grey have a surprise collision with Freedom Force, while Infectia sets Iceman in her sights!
description.70: Home at last! The FF finally makes their way back to Earth, but they barely have time to breathe before being ambushed by A.I.M.! But what are the sinister scientists trying to hide? And how is their reappearance connected to an old and powerful enemy?
description.71: Colossus has been having visions of his sister in terrible danger. The metal mutant heads to limbo to check up on her.
description.72: Following their departure from the Savage Land, the X-Men find themselves caught in the middle of a terrible storm at sea - and also find a Professor X in deadly danger! Can the mutant team save their beloved leader and mentor?
description.73: Blind Justice delivers brutal vigilante heroics but are his methods too severe for Hawkeye?  Plus, Dr. Pym in a solo adventure!
description.74: Julie Power lashes out against a girl gang!
description.76: Rob Little is flown out to the Chu Chi Twelfth Evac Hospital!
description.80: Peter Parker meets a fellow irradiated hero at a job interview. Who is Wes Cassaday, and how did he gain his abilities? Plus, Spidey runs afoul of Dr. Nero!
description.81: Now a full-blown Leviathan, the Avengers attempts to save Marrina, yet destroy the beast she has become. Dr. Pym comes up with a temporary solution involving Pym particles, but will they be able to save her life? Plus, the mysterious woman tormenting Dr. Druid turns out to be a member of the Kang Korps.
description.82: The Captain, D-Man, Falcon and Nomad versus the Viper and her legions! Plus: The new Captain America, John Walker, and Battle Star versus the most dangerous mutant force since the Brotherhood of Evil Mutants... the Resistants!
description.84: The origins of the sinister villain Tombstone are revealed!
description.85: Cap'n Reptyl stands triumphant over Surfer and Nova…but the battle’s not lost yet! Nenora’s Skrull identify is uncovered, but by who? The Contemplator meets a ruthless end.
description.86: During his time as Ant-Man, Hank Pym fought with many a sinister foe - and now, those foes have returned together for REVENGE! It's a grudge match years in the making - one that will all come down to WONDER MAN!
description.90: With the construction of a massive citadel by the Sun-People threatening the ecosystem of the Savage Land, the X-Men team up with KA-ZAR to prevent its destruction!
description.91: Attorney Matt Murdock faces the most challenging case of his career, a lawsuit that will bring justice to a boy blinded by corporate pollution. But Daredevil has an even bigger case- Typhoid Mary, a villain as intriguing as she is insane.
description.92: Rock and Redeemer attack the military facility that keeps the gamma rays bomb. Meanwhile, Betty Ross drops another kind of bomb on the Hulk...
description.93: The New Mutants attend Cypher's funeral, leading to emotional revelations for every surviving member, including Warlock.
description.94: Battle on two fronts! First, Thor must match his strength against the deadly new villain known only as Quicksand! Then, Hogun the Grim suffers a head injury which sends him on a rampage. And only one man stands in his way--Daredevil, the Man Without Fear!
description.96: Villainess Infectia seduces victims with a mutating kiss that turns any man, woman or child into a monstrous being and a mind-slave!
description.98: Stranded on a mystery planet with no way home! The new Fantastic Four will have their hands full trying to get back to Earth- especially with the demonic Master Pandemonium standing in their way!
description.99: Deep beneath the X-Men's Australian base, Longshot is beset by mysterious phantoms.

1.text: Wolverine investigates a criminal mobster named Roche in Madripoor's seedy underbelly. Tyger Tiger guest stars!

17.text: The scene shifts to Hong Kong as Nick and his allies travel overseas to learn more about the corruption that's eaten away at S.H.I.E.L.D.! Madame Hydra's on hand, too ... but is she friend or foe?

18.text: When a soldier-turned-slave falls in love with the Morituri's Toxin, he may have no choice but to undergo the deadly Morituri process himself!

19.text: As the Tet Offensive draws nearer, the men of the 23rd celebrate Thanksgiving in the field. But what they don't realize is that they're giving the enemy something to be thankful about, too!

20.text: A gang of criminals is smuggling illegal aliens into the country — but whether the aliens are alive or not when they get here is a different question! Can the Punisher, armed only with ancient weapons, put an end to the gang's vile schemes?

21.text: This group of young ninjas fights crime each day. How will they react when someone close to them dies?

23.text: Azania goes to war with Wakanda! After his vocal, (and physical), disapproval at Azania’s treatment of her black citizens, T’Challa stands poised to sacrifice his life.

26.text: The team's struggle against Quicksilver continues! And they have no idea what's coming for them next!

30.text: Spidey continues his search for Tombstone, but he soon discovers he's not alone in his search. Someone else has Tombstone in his sights, and he's not the type to show mercy! Watch out, Tombstone, the Punisher is on your trail!

31.text: Silver Surfer vs. Silver Surfer? One’s an imposter, one’s the real deal. And by the end of this issue, only one will stand triumphant!

43.text: The Silver Surfer is living as a homeless person on Earth when Galactus arrives, proclaims himself God and tells everyone to enjoy themselves. Chaos ensues! By the legendary Stan Lee and Moebius.

44.text: A wounded medic, Andy Clark, is awarded a Purple Heart. But it is a medal he believes others need more than he does! But complicating his desire to give the medal to those who deserve it is girl trouble -- South Vietnamese style!

45.text: Patsy Walker must confront the “Mad-Dog”, A.K.A. her childhood friend, Buzz Baxter!

46.text: After two millennia, a new Wolfpack rises! Meet their latest incarnation, a rag tag team of five young, street-smart ninjas, each gifted with remarkable abilities!

48.text: Black Panther deftly dissembles the Supremacists, a group of white Azanians who are terrorizing their nation by enforcing apartheid!

49.text: To aid in his battle against S.H.I.E.L.D., Fury recruits some unlikely allies — Tony Stark, an accountant, and one of the greatest villainesses in the world!

50.text: The Punisher and Daredevil may be tracking the same madman, but their different approaches in handling a murderer make them enemies in combat! Justice is dished out to the Punisher- will Frank Castle let DD have the final say?

55.text: Before the West Coast Avengers can even catch their breath from their last fight, they become captives of the deadly foe…QUICKSILVER!? What has caused the once-noble Avenger to turn on his comrades, including his own sister?

59.text: It's Tony Stark's worst nightmare! In a fevered dream-like state, Iron Man faces what he fears the most: his technology running rampant -- causing world war, death and destruction -- and it's all his fault! Will Tony turn back to the bottle or let the technology take control? See Iron Man vs. his greatest enemy: himself!

60.text: The Star Child does the unthinkable - by taking away Ken's Star Brand! What will this cost Ken, and what does the child plan to do with it?

61.text: Joe Robertson is bedridden in the hospital, gravely injured in his encounter with Tombstone. Shaken to his core, Peter Parker embarks on a solemn misson: find Tombstone and make him answer to justice, at any cost!

62.text: Ronan the Accuser comes to Nenora’s aid after a band of soldiers attempt mutiny. How much longer can the Skrull imposter maintain her ruse? Surfer finds a moment to mourn the death of Mantis, but is invigorated by a new mission- finding her son!

75.text: Nick Fury goes “Into the Depths” alongside Black Knight, Dr. Druid, She-Hulk, and Thor!

77.text: When the new Morituri find the late Vyking's tape recorder and autobiography, the stage is set for a landmark tale in the annals of the Morituri. All the loose ends surrounding the old Morituri are tied up, as the new generation prepares to take over - even though the fledgling heroes know it will cost them their lives!

79.text: Who is the Black Panther without the protection of their Panther Spirit? T’Challa must enter a trial by combat against the ‘White Ape’ to regain his title as Wakanda’s protector. A journey of mythic redemption starts here!

83.text: Iron Man, no more! With Tony Stark wounded and unable to don his armor, he decides to retire the Iron Man for good! But when Firepower goes rogue and attacks Stark Enterprises, Tony may have to don a new set of armor to stop him! Armor Wars concludes as Iron Man becomes a hero once more!

84.text: The origins of the sinister villain Tombstone are revealed!

85.text: Cap'n Reptyl stands triumphant over Surfer and Nova…but the battle’s not lost yet! Nenora’s Skrull identify is uncovered, but by who? The Contemplator meets a ruthless end.

86.text: During his time as Ant-Man, Hank Pym fought with many a sinister foe - and now, those foes have returned together for REVENGE! It's a grudge match years in the making - one that will all come down to WONDER MAN!
